<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_305_r1l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> her VVirıch / Als Jr vns <expan>embot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd cʒwen frıdbrief / vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r1l4">als ew vnſer <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von Hohenloch <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat geſant habt / Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r1l5">vvöllen wir das aufnemen / . vnd <expan>bit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew / daʒ Jr die ſıgelt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r1l6">fürbas ſchıcket / daʒ ſie <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hohenloch auch ſıgel / vnd vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r1l7">der ein <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> werde / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Marie Magdalene </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_305" id="152r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
